latestPosts.caption:
You create your thoughts ,Your thoughts create your intentions & your intentions create your reality, such is the power of manifestation ✨

This morning when i stepped out for the promo run @mumbai_halfmarathon, I had no idea what was awaiting for me at the holding area of wings sports club,as I am walking & exchanging greetings with some lovely running buddies, I stumbled upon face to face with this 'Larger than Life' sized promo poster of @pumaindia & @mumbai_halfmarathon featuring 'Me'😅, I momentarily froze for a few secs & had to literally pinch myself to acknowledge that 'girl in the poster' is really me 🤭. I am going to be forever grateful & thankful to @sunilshetty27 @sangy_31 @nebsports  @pumaindia for having me as an Ambassador & giving me this beautiful moment to smile & shine 🥰 & surely a one that i will cherish forever.

I have ran every single edition of this run since 2018 & it has always held a special place in my heart. So calling out all my friends & run fam to register for this one. 

#gratitude #gratefulheart #blessed

P. S. Do keep a watch out on my stories too for the announcements for the next promo run & also the registration details for the main event is in the link in my bio.
